  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study investigates the analgesic effect of different auditory inputs. Employing a
      within-subject design, the study includes healthy participants that are exposed to thermal
      stimuli while listening to three different auditory inputs. By repeating this on separate
      test days, the involvement of bodily processes is investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
